name: Mystery Belt
description:
Simple and elegant belt with a mystery braid (how DO they do it?) and a brass buckle.

Everything is done by hand here; from dyeing to waxing the thread. The edges are beveled and finished and exposed suede is burnished.

The leather will soften and form with use; Much like your favorite pair of jeans, it's up to you to wear it in. Each piece is designed to be perfectly understated and timeless. And that they will last, for all of time.

Please choose the leather colour in the options, and add a note indicating which colour of thread you'd like: black, brown, forest green, red, and light teal.

Free shipping on orders over 99$. Discount applied at checkout.

name: Custom mittens - designed from your own handprint
description:
These mittens will fit YOUR hands and your hands only!

- Made from premium leather for extra durability and insulated with lambswool and a silk/wool blend lining.
- A tight cuff to keep the warmth in and the snow out.
- Creasing areas and thumb are reinforced with extra leather pieces.
- Hardware at wrist to attach the mittens together for safe keeping.
- Includes an idiot string; don't lose them!
- Name tag in both mittens.
- Each pair has its own pattern, which I design right from a tracing of your hand.

Each pair is custom designed to match the measurements of your hand. Send me a tracing of your hands, and I'll make you a pair of mittens that will fit like Cinderella's slipper. Except on your hands. And made of silk and wool and leather ...

Send me said hand tracing via snail mail or email. Also send the name you'd like on the inside tags. I can have your mittens in the mail within 10-15 business days.

Free shipping does not apply to custom mittens, sorry! UNLESS you purchase another item from the shop, then it's free shipping for the whole order.

name: iPhone Wallet Skin
description:
Ready to go, just peel and stick.

A mash-up of the Nous Wallet and the iPhone skin. If a few cards and your keys are all you need to get out the door, this will eliminate one more thing to remember. 

The edges are beveled and slicked. The exposed suede is burnished.

The front of the skin is in three pieces. A top piece, a bottom piece and a home button piece. Without the arms on the sides like a typical phone skin, touchability remains intact in all four corners of your screen all the while protecting the screen from direct contact with surfaces. The home button is a separate piece; it's designed to be part of the skin like in the photos. 

Please choose the leather colour in the options, and add a note indicating which colour of thread you'd like: black, brown, forest green, red, and light teal.
